### Edit a storage device; Enter fdisk menu
fdisk  /dev/sdb

### Get help in fdisk menu
m

### add a new partition, 500 Mega Bytes
Command (m for help): n
Select (default p): p
Partition number (3,4, default 3): 3
First sector (2050048-25165823, default 2050048): 
Last sector, +/-sectors or +/-size{K,M,G,T,P} (2050048-25165823, default 25165823): +500M

### print the partition table
p

### change a partition type
t
